# nginx Package

Target: @TARGET_TRIPLE@

Components:

- nginx @NGINX_VERSION@
- OpenSSL @OPENSSL_VERSION@
- PCRE2 @PCRE2_VERSION@
- zlib @ZLIB_VERSION@
- curl @CURL_VERSION@ static client installed as bin/curl_static
- ngx_http_proxy_connect_module from @PROXY_CONNECT_REPO@, ref @PROXY_CONNECT_REF@, patch @PROXY_CONNECT_PATCH@

Feature intent:

- ECH-capable TLS stack through bundled OpenSSL 4.x.
- HTTP forward proxy CONNECT support through ngx_http_proxy_connect_module.
- Self-contained nginx binary with bundled OpenSSL, PCRE2, and zlib built from source.

Useful paths:

- sbin/nginx
- bin/curl_static
- conf/nginx.conf
- logs/
- run/
- install_service.sh / uninstall_service.sh for systemd on Linux
- install_service.cmd / uninstall_service.cmd for WinSW on Windows

Example:

```sh
./sbin/nginx -p "$(pwd)/" -c conf/nginx.conf
```

Service install examples:

```sh
sudo ./install_service.sh nginx nginx
sudo systemctl start nginx
```

```cmd
install_service.cmd nginx
net start nginx
```
